  itemName: Robe of the Archmagi
  itemIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0be9e27eb6c82ea49929212978c2167e, type: 3}
  description: 'Increases Magic Resist by 10 and Ability Power by 40. Grants "Arcane
    Mastery": Every time the wearer casts an ability, their Ability Power increases
    by 10% for the rest of the combat (stacks infinitely). Additionally, the wearer
    gains a not stackable shield equal to 20% of their max mana for 3 seconds after
    every cast. A magnificent garment of deep indigo silk, embroidered with shifting
    constellations; it hums with the collected wisdom of a thousand years, shielding
    the master from harm while fueling their ever-growing magical dominance.'
